==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Incognizable
<hw>In*cog"ni*za*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not
cognizable; incapable of being recognized, known, or
distinguished.</def> <rj><au>H. Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The Lettish race, not a primitive stock of the Slavi, but a
distinct branch, now become <qex>incognizable</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Tooke.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Incognizance</ent>⟦br⟧
